For [hostInfo](manual/reference/command/hostinfo) command, Atlas Data Federation
returns only the following subset of fields from the standard MongoDB
response:

```json
{
  "ok" : <return>,
  "system" : {
    "currentTime" : ISODate("<timestamp>"),
    "hostname" : "<hostname>",
    "cpuAddrSize" : <number>,
    "memSizeMB" : <number>,
    "numCores" : <number>,
    "cpuArch" : "<identifier>",
  },
  "os" : {
    "type" : "<string>",
    "name" : "<string>",
  },
  "extra" : { }
}
```
